rom a triple-double!\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This could have been the first triple-double by any rookie in WNBA history.\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1545, \"end\": 1549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999786336959, \"rank\": 1.9337263115881854e-08, \"text\": \"WNBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Fever won the game despite their awful coach.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Recall that Diana Taurasi talked sh*t about Caitlin, saying, \\\"Reality is coming.\\\"\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Diana Taurasi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\"}, {\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9997622754583533, \"rank\": 0.00022093606564626008, \"text\": \"Caitlin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Thomas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, Grandma Taurasi, the oldest active player in the WNBA, had a reality check.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1709, \"end\": 1716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.246067067290971e-24, \"text\": \"Taurasi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/